 Hurling The Gaelic Athletic Association is an Irish international amateur sporting and cultural organisation. Football 2017-Present Gaelic football (Irish: Peil Ghaelach; short name Peil or Caid), commonly referred to as football or Gaelic, is an Irish team sport. It is played between two teams of 15 players on a rectangular grass pitch.
